  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd 203 \u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcb \u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bb3 \u0b95\u0b9e\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbe \u0baa\u0bca\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A man was arrested with 203 kg Kerala Ganja packets in Mannar's Iluppaikadavai area",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "About 203 kg packs of Kerala ganja have been seized at Ilubai Pass in Mannar-Mantai West Divisional Secretary Division.",
        "The Kerala Ganja packets were seized during a special round-up conducted by the naval camp officials at Munga yesterday (11) Monday evening.",
        "The police said that when a suspicious boat was raided, Kerala ganja packets were seized while hidden in it.",
        "A 45-year-old man from Velangkulam has been arrested in connection with the incident.",
        "In this case, steps have been taken to produce the suspect in the Mannar court and Iluphaikadavai police are conducting further investigations into the incident."
      ],
